The API v2 Authentication is implemented as HTTP Basic Authentication over SSL (HTTPS).  *Your API login credentials are not the same as the credentials you use to log in to the web interface*.  You must obtain your API credentials separately.


h3. Obtaining Your API Credentials

Your API v2 id and password can be generated from the "Chargify Direct" link in the "Settings" tab of your seller dashboard.

Your @client_id@ is your Chargify Direct API ID.

Your @client_secret@ is your Chargify Direct password.

h3. Example Call For API v2

<pre>
  <code>curl -X GET -d "client_id=<API_ID>&client_secret=<DIRECT_PASSWORD>" https://api.chargify.com/api/v2/products</code>
</pre>
